      • createProxyPort

        <S extends Service,P> P createProxyPort(Credentials credentials,
                                      LoginWebService loginWebService,
                                      Service service,
                                      Class<P> portType)
        Create a proxy based port. This port will be able to perform auto logins, re-logins, etc.
        Type Parameters:
        S - the type of web service being used.
        P - the type of port desired.
        Parameters:
        credentials - our login credentials.
        loginWebService - used for logins and session ids.
        service - contains the port for web service calls.
        portType - the type of port to perform web service calls.
        Returns:
        a session based port.
